definition: between/among/within a definite time or space/room/section of a room or lateral space between two pairs of pillars/classifier for rooms
gap/to separate/to thin out (seedlings)/to sow discontent
Hmong or Miao ethnic group of southwest China/surname Miao

sentences.english: Mother is in the garden thinning out the onion plants; she should have a good crop this year.
sentences.chinese: 媽媽在花園裏對洋蔥進行間苗，今年定會豐收。
